fields_description.Start Time: Exam start time (24-hour format, first in range)
fields_description.End Time: Exam end time (24-hour format, last in range)
fields_description.Page Number: Page number from which the entry was extracted
fields_description.Line Number: Line number from which the entry was extracted
fields_description.RowText: Full concatenated text of the row as it appears in the PDF
fields_description.BoundingBox: Coordinates of the row in the PDF (x0, y0, x1, y1)
